# SCOPE GUARDRAILS (Hard)

## Allowed (always)
- Content expansion and proofreading to become a go-to learning resource
- Theory animations (teaching-first, user-triggered)
- 2D/3D practice demos aligned to theory
- CMS seeding/validation/audit for completeness of 12 topics
- Code quality improvements + dead code removal
- Remove any login/auth gating from public pages

## Forbidden unless explicitly requested
- accounts/auth, payments, comments/community
- analytics integrations
- gamification/leaderboards
- unrelated large redesign during content tasks
